.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-TXO-SPEND" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-txo-spend \- spend a specific on-chain output (UTXO)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-txo-spend
.I txid
.I output
.I destination
.SH DESCRIPTION
Spends the UTXO at
.IR txid : output
by constructing a withdrawal transaction to
.IR destination ,
using
.B lightning-cli withdraw
with a UTXO filter.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true,"txid":...,"tx":...}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-utxo-list (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-sweep (1)
